{"tid":1467077,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"幾嬲都好，唔可以阻救護去救人呀！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:35.000Z","uid":299988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b1dda1e04a3b5935eaeb8fe57b094514a4584af","tid":1467077,"uid":299988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:01.000Z","msg":"唔好咁激動咁衝動啦！！！<br />\n我知大家都好憤怒好想打死啲鬼同班仆街<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">咁樣係唔會令到佢地驚架</span></span>！！<br />\n<br />\n發現有鬼<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>制服左</strong></span>就好喇！<br />\n點解仲要圍毆？<br />\n仲<span style=\"color: purple;\">阻住啲救援人員！</span><br />\n咁你地同721班白衫有咩分別？？<br />\n<br />\n唔可以咁樣架！！！<br />\n打撚死左佢都唔會有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>成功</strong></span>！<br />\n打撚死左佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">個女仔都唔會有番隻眼</span></strong>！<br />\n純粹係發洩咋！！<br />\n同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警</span></span></span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有咩分別</span></strong></span>呀！！？？？<br />\n當你地屌緊黑警<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺紅了眼</span></span>既時候你地都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">做緊同一樣野</span></span>！！<br />\n<br />\n捉到鬼係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>好叻</strong></span>，但唔可以一捉到鬼就<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">失晒控</span></span></span>！<br />\n我地每一個人都好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n但真係唔好再<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">比情緒帶住走蓋過理智</span></span>啊！<br />\n<br />\n大家好辛苦先行到今日呢一步<br />\n唔可以失去理智失去信念<br />\n好好記住梁天琦封信講既野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HaouXEk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHaouXEk.png&h=ef52670b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yf3iQZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyf3iQZn.png&h=fee92d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每一步都好緊要！<br />\n我地要話比人知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有暴徒</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有暴政</span></span>！！！<br />\n我地同黑警唔同既地方，係<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地有人性</strong></span></span><br />\n佢地無呀！<br />\n<br />\n所以我跪求大家<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">- 一定要控制好情緒<br />\n- 有咩事幫手㩒住身體既人<br />\n- 理智行先<br />\n- 唔好太衝動<br />\n- 唔可以阻住救援(無論救邊個:黑警又好/鬼又好/狗又好)<br />\n- 唔可以襲擊救護<br />\n- 唔好屌救護點解要救啲仆街,因為呢個係佢哋嘅職責</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔係要割蓆<br />\n唔會去指責<br />\n只係希望大家都可以做得更好<br />\n岩既繼續做<br />\n唔岩既，盡量做岩佢囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5ad8694dc721e7e86225f99f00ed45a09654cd","tid":1467077,"uid":299988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1f389cd94730872c72daefccc4287381f31173b","tid":1467077,"uid":299988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}